FBIS4-48477 "drafr098_e_94010" FBIS-AFR-94-098 Daily Report 19 May 1994 WEST AFRICA Niger Sentences Given to Opposition Activists Sentences Given to Opposition Activists AB1905154994 Libreville Africa No. 1 in French 1215 GMT 19 May 94 AB1905154994 Libreville Africa No. 1 French BFN [Text] Thirteen opposition activists arrested during the April demonstrations in Niamey were this morning given three-month suspended sentences and three-month imprisonment terms.
